{"comments":"NumberEditor — Bounded number input with slider.\n\n## Design\n\nEvery number in Hydrogen is bounded. This editor enforces bounds at the\ntype level and clamps values in the UI. Features:\n\n- Slider for quick adjustment\n- Number input for precise values\n- Step buttons for increment/decrement\n- Visual indication of bounds\n\n## Schema Integration\n\nAccepts bounds from Schema atoms:\n- Roughness (0.0-1.0)\n- Opacity (0-100)\n- Elevation (0-24)\n- Corner radius (0-9999)\n\nValues are ALWAYS clamped to bounds. Invalid states are unrepresentable.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Render a bounded number editor.\n\nFeatures slider + number input. Values are always clamped to bounds.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound","ContextMenu","NumberEditor"],"NumberEditorProp"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"tag":"ParensInType"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Element","Types"],"Element"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":"msg","tag":"TypeVar"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},"visibility":"TypeVarInvisible"},"tag":"ForAll"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[217,74],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/ContextMenu/NumberEditor.purs","start":[217,1]},"title":"numberEditor"},{"children":[],"comments":"Render a bounded integer editor.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":{"identifier":"msg","kind":null,"skolem":null,"ty